def get_ct(df,var, var2):
    ct_res = pd.crosstab(df[var], df[var2], margins = True)
    return ct_res.drop(columns = 'All')

EDA Comments¶

1. Customers with secondary education hold more term deposit account compared to other marital status
2. Majority of the customers fall under the age group 30 to 40
3. Customers with Management job hold more term deposit account compared to other job category
4. Customers who have no housing loan hold more term deposit account compared to no housing loan
5. Customer who did not default the loan subscribed to term deposit in larger number compared to defaulted ones

In [32]:
#Let's drop the rows whose call duration is less than 10s
convertedDF.drop(convertedDF[convertedDF["duration"] < 10/60].index, axis = 0, inplace = True)

#Let's drop contact column. It does not matter how the customer is contacted
if 'contact' in convertedDF.columns:
    convertedDF.drop('contact',axis=1,inplace=True)
    
convertedDF["y"].replace({"no":0,"yes":1},inplace=True)

catcols1 = ['job', 'marital', 'education', 'default', 'housing', 'loan','poutcome','day','month']
for col  in catcols1:
    convertedDF[col] = convertedDF[col].astype('category')
convertedDF.info()

X = convertedDF.drop('y', axis=1)
Y = convertedDF['y']

X = pd.get_dummies(X,drop_first=True)
X.head()

In [34]:
def draw_cm( actual, predicted ):
    cm = confusion_matrix( actual, predicted)
    sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True,  fmt='.2f', xticklabels = [0,1] , yticklabels = [0,1] )
    plt.ylabel('Observed')
    plt.xlabel('Predicted')
    plt.show()

Logistic Regression Algorithm¶

In [35]:
logreg = LogisticRegression(random_state=7)
logreg.fit(X_train, y_train) 

pred_train = logreg.predict(X_train)
mat_train = confusion_matrix(y_train, pred_train)
print("confusion matrix [Training]  = \n", mat_train)

y_predict = logreg.predict(X_test)
mat_test = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_predict)
print("confusion matrix [Testing] = \n", mat_test)

lr_train_accuracy = logreg.score(X_train,y_train)
lr_test_accuracy  = logreg.score(X_test, y_test)
lr_recall_score   = recall_score(y_test,y_predict)
lr_precision_score = precision_score(y_test,y_predict)
lr_f1_score       = f1_score(y_test,y_predict)
lr_roc_auc_score  = roc_auc_score(y_test,y_predict)

print("Training Accuracy : ",lr_train_accuracy)  
print()
print("Testing Accuracy : ",lr_test_accuracy)
print()
print("Confusion Matrix : ")
print(draw_cm(y_test,y_predict))
print()
print("Recall : ",lr_recall_score)
print()
print("Precision : ",lr_precision_score)
print()
print("F1 Score : ",lr_f1_score)
print()
print("Roc Auc Score : ",lr_roc_auc_score)
